/*
# Import all Polibox products with real CDN image URLs

1. What this does
- Inserts 78 products from polibox.com.br with verified real image URLs from the Polibox CDN
- Each product has a main image_url and gallery_images (up to 4 additional images)
- Products are categorized into existing categories and assigned to existing brands
- Uses ON CONFLICT (slug) DO UPDATE to update image URLs if product already exists
2. Security
- No schema changes. Only INSERT statements into existing products table.
- Uses SELECT FROM brands/categories to get IDs by slug (no hardcoded IDs).
*/
